      <title>外国首席执行官对在华商业信心略有增强</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/foreign-ceos-slightly-more-confident-about-business-in-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管对经济和地缘政治紧张局势加剧的担忧迫使许多人重新评估自己的存在，但今年上半年，在华外国高管对中国大陆的信心略有增强。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/foreign-ceos-slightly-more-confident-about-business-in-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
